WEBVTT

00:00:00.585 --> 00:00:03.633
-erman film numer zeks.

00:00:05.243 --> 00:00:10.265
zogt mir, ir dermont zikh di rayze keyn Amerike?

00:00:10.525 --> 00:00:13.506
oyf der shif? dertseylt mir.

00:00:10.677 --> 00:00:13.691
ye ye ye.

00:00:15.148 --> 00:00:24.376
vu ikh bin geforn, fun Doytshland iz geforn shifn in di ⟨LAKE⟩ in di UNK o Kenzes Siti eyn mol a monat.

00:00:24.376 --> 00:00:27.664
Nyu York geforn mer oft. ikh bin geforn keyn Nyu Orlins.

00:00:27.855 --> 00:00:37.130
iz geven a zeyer a sakh litviner, ukrainer, und nisht keyn yidn-fraynt.

00:00:37.288 --> 00:00:40.032
nisht keyn yidn-fraynt oykhet. a gantse shif.

00:00:40.090 --> 00:00:48.133
shoyn, m'iz ongekumen, bin ikh ongekumen Nyu Orlins, a BAND muzik hot geshpilt, m'hot undz oyfgenumen zeyer fayn di amerikaner,

00:00:48.443 --> 00:00:54.917
und un fun dort hob ikh gezolt forn mit di ban,

00:00:55.041 --> 00:00:59.962
ye un di Dzhoynt hot undz opgevart. di yidn hot der Dzhoynt opgevart.

00:01:00.255 --> 00:01:04.496
un m'hot un ye un azo- dos vil ikh nokh zogn, oyf di shif iz geven a yidishe meydl,

00:01:04.496 --> 00:01:09.699
vos zi iz shtendik ibergegebn oyf di Landsbrik oyf di shif, bin ikh geganen arbetn.

00:01:09.925 --> 00:01:13.867
m'ho- zey hobn undz gezogt az s'geyt eyn mol a monat di shif.

00:01:14.481 --> 00:01:21.056
un un yetst farshtey ikh di BUSINESS far vos, un zey hobn nisht genug HELP,

00:01:21.282 --> 00:01:26.085
az ver es vil voluntirn tsu arbetn vet aroyfgeyn a tog frier oyf di shif.

00:01:26.496 --> 00:01:29.210
ikh hob nisht gevolt voluntirn, ikh hob shoyn gehat genug mit arbet,

00:01:29.210 --> 00:01:31.395
ikh hob getrakht ikh hob tsayt nokh eyn tog.

00:01:31.395 --> 00:01:34.826
ober s'geven a sakh, zey hobn voluntirt, zey hobn gevolt aroyfgeyn oyf di shif.

00:01:35.068 --> 00:01:43.331
zenen aroyfgeganen oyf di shif frier, un nakher zenen zey gevorn SEASICK.

00:01:43.523 --> 00:01:49.558
zenen m'hot m'hot gefregt deye tsimer ken men frier esn, nakher hobn zey gezogt, kumts ver s'iz greyt.

00:01:50.813 --> 00:01:54.772
s'geven a militerishe shif. U.S.S. Heri Teyler.

00:01:54.829 --> 00:01:59.193
ikh hob zikh mitgenumen, zey hobn gezogt a lemon s'gut far nisht tsu vern krank.

00:01:59.284 --> 00:02:03.811
hob ikh zikh mitgenumen tsvelef lemons, hob ikh zey tseteylt,

00:02:03.811 --> 00:02:06.601
eyns hob ikh zikh gelozt far mir far EMERGENCY,

00:02:06.878 --> 00:02:10.314
iz arayngebrengt keyn Amerike farfoylt, ikh hob es nisht badorfn.

00:02:10.336 --> 00:02:12.410
ikh bin nor geven hungerik, ikh hob gegesn.

00:02:12.410 --> 00:02:15.681
ikh az ikh hob nisht ge- gut gefilt iz nor ven ikh hob geven hungerik.

00:02:15.788 --> 00:02:17.362
ikh hob gehat a gute rayze.

00:02:17.362 --> 00:02:21.064
BUT di antisemitn hobn ongehoybn tsu lakhn fun di yidishe meydl, fun dem,

00:02:21.525 --> 00:02:26.953
hot zi zikh gekent mit dem CAPTAIN fun di shif, hot er arayngerufn C.I.A. er hot a komunist oyf di shift.

00:02:27.094 --> 00:02:31.644
oyf dem ukrai- a ukrainer oder litviner iz es geven. iz geforn tsu a mame.

00:02:31.870 --> 00:02:36.389
zey hobn ir gezogt az ven er hot ongekumen hobn zey im shoyn gevart tsu intervyuirn.

00:02:36.389 --> 00:02:39.086
a komunist iz geven zeyer shlekht in,

00:02:39.582 --> 00:02:45.229
azoy hob ikh bald gezen az far di yidn hobn do a deye tsu zogn in Amerike, hob ikh shoyn gezen s'gut.

00:02:45.758 --> 00:02:53.311
un m'hot mikh opgevart, zey hobn undz gegebn tsu esn. nakher hot men mikh aroyfgezetst oyf a ban tsu forn nokh Topika Kenzes.

00:02:53.672 --> 00:02:59.437
zogt mir, ven ir hot zikh dervust az ayer az zayer bruder lebt,

00:03:00.287 --> 00:03:01.496
vi azoy?

00:03:01.182 --> 00:03:03.741
vi azoy un bashraybt mir dem moment.

00:03:04.202 --> 00:03:09.236
ven ikh hob zikh dervust er iz, ikh denk Kedi iz es geven.

00:03:09.236 --> 00:03:15.502
ikh hob a kuzin, ven ikh hob getrofn mayn kuzin oyf di ban stantsye,

00:03:15.525 --> 00:03:20.564
un er hot mir shoyn gezogt az der bruder lebt, er iz in Shvedn, er hot mir fartseylt.

00:03:21.043 --> 00:03:26.420
un hob ikh ge- hot er mir gezogt fun van er iz opgeforn, hob ikh ongeshribn a briv,

00:03:26.460 --> 00:03:31.013
iz zayn nomen, di ban nomen, un oyfgeshribn Shvedn. ikh hob gevust s'geven,

00:03:31.013 --> 00:03:35.232
un ikh hob es geshikt, eyner iz geforn dort ahin keyn Libek vu er iz avekgeforn,

00:03:35.232 --> 00:03:42.316
zoln arayn in yidishe organizatsye, tsum Dzhoynt un zogn zoln dos shikn mitn Roytn Kroyts dem briv tsu im.

00:03:42.475 --> 00:03:47.919
un zey hobn dos ibergeshikt keyn Shvedn, un er im derhaltn dem briv. ye.

00:03:48.111 --> 00:03:51.750
un er hot mir shoyn geshribn fun onkl, ikh hob shoyn geshribn tsum onkl,

00:03:51.807 --> 00:03:55.817
un oyf azoy lang s'geven kontakt un m'hot zikh geshribn.

00:03:56.498 --> 00:03:59.226
ven zent ir ongekumen keyn Amerike?

00:03:59.637 --> 00:04:05.250
APRIL gloyb ikh der FIFTH, fiftn APRIL nayntsn nayn un fertsik.

00:04:05.762 --> 00:04:09.029
ven hot ir zikh bakent mir ayer froy?

00:04:09.222 --> 00:04:14.362
mayn froy iz geven in in di yor zibn un zekhtsik.

00:04:16.022 --> 00:04:18.159
zi iz oykh a UNK?

00:04:16.933 --> 00:04:23.424
zi zi iz geven in di milkhome AS a kristlekhe, AS a shikse.

00:04:23.582 --> 00:04:30.208
m'hot ire, zi hot mir fartseylt, zi ken nisht redn derfun, az ziers a yingere shvester hobn di polyakn geshosn,

00:04:30.332 --> 00:04:32.266
un a bruder hobn zey geshosn.

00:04:32.307 --> 00:04:34.764
un di eltern zenen gegangen nokh Treblinka.

00:04:34.922 --> 00:04:39.067
un zi hot a goy epes genumen, oykhet a polke geratevet zi,

00:04:39.073 --> 00:04:43.339
eyne iz nisht geforn hot zi genumen oyf yenem's ort, oyf a tsveyte nomen,

00:04:43.339 --> 00:04:49.057
un zi kukt oys vi a poylishe shikse, AND iz zi geforn keyn Doytshland arbetn.

00:04:49.080 --> 00:04:50.947
vi heyst ayer froy?

00:04:52.216 --> 00:05:01.089
Khanka Honikman, fun di fun di MADEN'S NAME. Honikman.

00:05:01.821 --> 00:05:06.236
zogt mir vi azoy iz haynt ayer lebn?

00:05:06.681 --> 00:05:07.907
vos?

00:05:07.474 --> 00:05:11.973
vi azoy iz haynt ayer lebn? vi azoy un vos tut ir haynt?

00:05:12.469 --> 00:05:15.635
haynt bin ikh ovulirt shoyn. ikh arbet shoyn nisht mer,

00:05:15.726 --> 00:05:17.964
un yetst bet men nor tsu zayn gezunt,

00:05:18.223 --> 00:05:25.288
und un dos bay undz di ibergeblibene zogt men az dos ales bay undz geshenkte yorn.

00:05:25.395 --> 00:05:32.766
vi la- vos m'lebt iz vi geshenkt far undz fun got. oyb s'do a got. veys ikh nisht.

00:05:32.766 --> 00:05:34.940
mit di tfiln vel ikh dir fartseyln.

00:05:35.976 --> 00:05:41.854
ikh hob ikh hob gegloybt, in der heym hob ikh geve- frum, ikh hob gedavnt dray mol a tog.

00:05:41.854 --> 00:05:43.449
ven ikh bin gegangen davenen,

00:05:43.449 --> 00:05:49.228
un ikh bin tsugekumen tsu di seyfer-toyres azoy vi s'volt geven azoy vi Moyshe Rabeyne gekumen in barg, azoy vi m'tsaygt

00:05:49.228 --> 00:05:51.495
in di pelikulas Moyshe gekumen.

00:05:51.788 --> 00:05:57.806
un azoy moyredik, s'gekumen yomkiper ikh hob moyre gehat. zeyer yidish geshtumt.

00:05:57.964 --> 00:06:00.084
BUT ikh bin gekumen in lager arayn,

00:06:00.090 --> 00:06:04.432
ven zey hobn gezogt m'zol opgebn di gold un zilber un ale vert zakhn,

00:06:04.432 --> 00:06:08.386
un zey hobn gezukht bay undz dos gelt, hob ikh gehat di tfiln.

00:06:08.393 --> 00:06:13.247
iz gekumen der S. ikh denk s'geven a doytsh, oder der ukrainer,

00:06:13.270 --> 00:06:19.811
mit zayn bayonet, gegebn a hak iber di tfiln oyf di helft, gezukht gelt, un er hot es gevorfn tsu di bazura.

00:06:20.290 --> 00:06:22.393
un s'hot gornisht pasirt tsu im.

00:06:22.804 --> 00:06:26.578
un den nokh a zakh, ven m'hot aroysgeshikt di yidn fun Tshmelev,

00:06:26.601 --> 00:06:32.450
ven zey hobn ale dos gantse shtetl gegangen tsum ro- rebn, in di in di shul arayn,

00:06:32.473 --> 00:06:39.555
m'hot oyfgemakht di Shulkhn Orekh, bay di seyfer-toyres un m'hot ale geveynt, un gebetn tsu got,

00:06:40.084 --> 00:06:46.710
un ikh hob gezen vi dem rebn hobn zey a mol genumen un oysgetsupt di bord un arayngezetst a mamkev tsum genumen far propagande,

00:06:46.767 --> 00:06:53.324
ikh hob di ale zakhn gezen. ikh hob gezen in Aushvits vi m'brent di yidn. un keyner redt gornisht.

00:06:55.035 --> 00:07:01.054
bin ikh shoyn fartsveyflt tsi efsher undzer got, tsi er klert fun undz tsi s'do a got.

00:07:01.330 --> 00:07:08.245
un ikh gey nokh yede yor gey ikh tsum davenen, rosheshone yomkiper, vayl s'iz in mir.

00:07:08.245 --> 00:07:11.921
BECAUSE, nisht BECAUSE ikh gey ikh gloyb nokh azoy in a got,

00:07:12.028 --> 00:07:15.248
vayl di mame hot mikh gelernt azoy un der tate, derfar gey ikh.

00:07:15.248 --> 00:07:20.443
ober in mir ikh zol zayn azoy religyez, bin ikh shoyn nisht.

00:07:20.652 --> 00:07:25.202
ikh bin nisht dergegn s'zol tsurikkumen tsu mir, vayl ikh hob geglikhn dos lebn.

00:07:25.461 --> 00:07:26.875
a MATTER OF FACT,

00:07:26.875 --> 00:07:31.423
di gants- ikh zog dos tsu rabeyim oykhet. dem RABBI ikh hob im gezogt,

00:07:31.423 --> 00:07:35.110
der RABBI vos ikh hob im gegebn a bisl ekstre esn in Aushvits,

00:07:35.110 --> 00:07:37.911
hob i- hot er mikh gefregt tsi ikh davn yedn, ikh hob im gezogt NO.

00:07:37.911 --> 00:07:41.435
er hot mir gegebn a siderl ikh zol davenen. ikh hob dos siderl.

00:07:41.965 --> 00:07:47.156
un un es ligt in mir dos yidishkeyt az tsvey yor tsurik,

00:07:47.331 --> 00:07:52.337
ikh hob a a voynung in di berg dort vu ale yidn forn, in di Ketskils,

00:07:52.427 --> 00:07:56.926
dort do a frumer vos farkoyfn di ale yidishe zakhn, tfiln.

00:07:57.507 --> 00:08:00.555
bin ikh gegangen ikh hob zikh gekoyft nokh a mol a por tfiln yetst.

00:08:02.434 --> 00:08:05.803
ikh davn nisht mit zey yeder tog. ikh greyt zikh tsu.

00:08:05.826 --> 00:08:09.330
ikh hob a tales, a tales kotn hob ikh, ikh trog es nisht,

00:08:09.572 --> 00:08:14.679
BUT ikh volt gevolt lebn tsurik dos lebn vos ikh hob gelebt in Tshmelev,

00:08:14.736 --> 00:08:19.776
es benkt zikh mir nokh dem. ober, dos yetst vil nisht kumen.

00:08:20.423 --> 00:08:26.407
vi azoy klert ir hot baaynflust ayer lebn alts vos ir hot ibergelebt?

00:08:29.063 --> 00:08:31.065
vos hot gemakht a ayndruk?

00:08:31.223 --> 00:08:37.950
der ayndruk iz, az m'klert arayn, m'hot farloyrn di yugnt, m'hot nisht gehat keyn yugnt,

00:08:38.142 --> 00:08:41.680
farloyrn, ikh bin tsurikgeforn nokh di krig keyn Tshmelev,

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:49.020
bin ikh ven ikh hob gegangen tsu di polyakn, zi hot mikh arayngelozt, nokh gut zi hot mikh arayngelozt in dem tsimer vu ikh bin geboyrn,

00:08:49.853 --> 00:08:57.157
ikh bin geganen tsu di voynunger vu mayn mame hot gevoynt, der tate, mayne onkls, mayne kuzinen.

00:08:57.157 --> 00:09:03.448
keyner iz nisht geblibn lebn. di di gebaydes shteyen dort, keyn yid iz nishto,

00:09:04.821 --> 00:09:07.025
iz vos far a firn ken dos zayn?

00:09:08.213 --> 00:09:10.670
demolts ikh hob nor gezogt kadesh un THAT'S IT.

00:09:11.858 --> 00:09:16.897
far vos rekhnt ir zent ir lebn geblibn?

00:09:18.422 --> 00:09:20.475
un dos di frume fregn mikh.

00:09:20.785 --> 00:09:26.803
a nes? ikh veys nisht, ikh veys nisht far vos. a mazl zakh. ikh veys nisht.

00:09:27.750 --> 00:09:28.880
ven hot ir,

00:09:27.771 --> 00:09:31.055
ikh ken nisht entfern dos. BUT gey, ikh veys nisht far vos ikh bin lebn geblibn.

00:09:31.348 --> 00:09:37.485
vayl di frume hot men umgebrengt. vos bin ikh geven azo tsadik? ikh veys nisht far vos.

00:09:38.419 --> 00:09:42.581
ven hot ir zikh getrofn tsum ershtn mol mit ayer bruder?

00:09:43.195 --> 00:09:47.475
in ven ikh hob zikh ongezamlt a bisl gelt in Nyu York,

00:09:47.481 --> 00:09:50.175
di ershte zakh zog ikh lomikh zen mayn bruder.

00:09:50.248 --> 00:09:55.439
un dos hot gemuzt zayn yor nayntsn akht un fuftsik bin ikh aher gekumen oyf Boynes Ayres.

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:57.020
dos ershte mol hot men zikh getrofn.

00:09:56.408 --> 00:09:57.590
dermont mir,

00:09:57.032 --> 00:10:00.249
ye geshribn hot men zikh ye.

00:10:00.205 --> 00:10:02.949
dermont mir ayer bruder's nomen.

00:10:03.850 --> 00:10:07.911
Hershl in der heym hot men im gerufn Hasha.

00:10:09.098 --> 00:10:12.467
Sherman, Hasha. undz rufn nokh Hasha haynt oykhet.

00:10:12.793 --> 00:10:18.053
di nomen iz in hebreish Tsvi, un Hershl.

00:10:18.261 --> 00:10:22.659
BUT in der heym hot men im gerufn azoy a a nomen vi a kind, Hasha.

00:10:23.678 --> 00:10:32.919
ir ir vilt epes zogn farn farn di kumendike doyres, far emetser vos zol hern ayere verter?

00:10:36.030 --> 00:10:39.130
koydem koydem vil ikh zogn azoy.

00:10:41.093 --> 00:10:44.917
az s'zol nisht mer forkumen dos.

00:10:45.885 --> 00:10:49.524
koydem vil ikh zogn azoy, a has zol mir hobn geblibn in mir

00:10:49.530 --> 00:10:56.004
gegn andere natsyonen LIKE vi vi polyakn, gegn ale,

00:10:56.078 --> 00:11:01.185
oder gegn ale doytshn, oder gegn ale ukrainer, trog ikh nisht, nisht gegn ale.

00:11:01.191 --> 00:11:07.445
afiles in yetstike tsayt, az ikh ken helfn a a a polyak helf ikh im.

00:11:07.738 --> 00:11:14.603
ober oyb eyner ver ikh gevoyer iz a antisemit, er hast a yid, di glaykh ikh nit. ikh hof

00:11:14.603 --> 00:11:19.055
ikh hof az zey ebn zikh fun di HISTORY lernen, di ale antisemitn,

00:11:19.078 --> 00:11:23.226
az zey tuen gornisht oyf mit dem antisemitishkeyt,

00:11:23.226 --> 00:11:30.913
az zey hobn getun a zakh azo kleyn vi m'zogt, vos s'iz meglekh tsu bashraybn.

00:11:30.913 --> 00:11:38.119
aza mayn HISTORY vos ikh hob do gegebn, iz hob ikh nisht enk gegebn ales, ven ikh gib enk ales,

00:11:38.119 --> 00:11:43.052
volt ets nisht gekent zikh tsuhern tsu dem, un ikh volt nisht gekent redn, ikh volt zikh tseveynt zeyer a sakh.

00:11:43.159 --> 00:11:45.009
hob ikh a sakh tsurikgehaltn.

00:11:45.083 --> 00:11:51.624
un ven m'shraybt bikher derfun, ven m'shraybt den on yeder eyner fun undz vos zey hobn getun,

00:11:52.305 --> 00:11:58.301
volt mentshn nisht gegloybt. oyb eyner volt gegloybt, volt er es nisht gekent leyenen derfun.

00:11:58.301 --> 00:12:03.504
azoy shlekht tsen mol erger vos er hot gezen Shindler's List.

00:12:03.848 --> 00:12:06.947
un vos er do, vos undz fartseyl'mir di mayses

00:12:07.020 --> 00:12:12.684
iz geven toyznt mol arger vos zey hobn getun tsu di yidn, tsu dem yidishn folk.

00:12:12.724 --> 00:12:16.206
un a danke got s'geblibn a bisl yidn lebn.

00:12:16.206 --> 00:12:21.864
un un un dos vos ikh hob gevolt nor blaybn lebn, ikh veys nisht far vos, efsher iz es a got's zakh,

00:12:21.938 --> 00:12:27.450
ikh zol kenen fartseyln di mayses tsu di velt vos zey hobn getun.

00:12:27.895 --> 00:12:32.760
ikh bin geven in Aushvits hob ikh nor gebetn ikh zol kenen tsaygn vos zey hobn getun mit a NUMBERS,

00:12:32.760 --> 00:12:37.147
un vi zey hobn undz bahandlt, vos zey hobn getun tsu di yidishn folk,

00:12:37.147 --> 00:12:40.460
un ikh hof un ikh gloyb az zey zen, zey ebn aynzen,

00:12:40.500 --> 00:12:45.523
az s'iz geven a groyse groyse CRIME un s- un s'zol zikh nisht iberkhazern mer.

00:12:45.681 --> 00:12:47.919
nisht bloyz far di yidn, far keynem nisht.

00:12:49.022 --> 00:12:51.108
d- dos iz ales vos ken ikh zogn.

00:12:50.743 --> 00:12:55.344
ir vilt nokh epes tsugebn fun dem vos ikh hob aykh nisht gefregt?

00:12:58.708 --> 00:13:05.249
ikh vel enk zogn, ven ikh bin geforn keyn Tshmelev, keygn zogn nokh mer zakhn,

00:13:05.323 --> 00:13:10.447
hob ikh gezogt, ikh vel aheymforn keyn Tshmelev, ikh vel nemen bilder ven m'hot undz aroysgeyogt.

00:13:11.230 --> 00:13:15.088
hob ikh geven, ikh bin un yetst oykhet, a pinktlekher.

00:13:15.094 --> 00:13:19.627
m'hot gezogt zekser, hob ikh gezogt geyogt di mamen un zey ale, kum aroys! kum aroys! kum aroys!

00:13:19.819 --> 00:13:23.357
un m'iz aroysgegangen hot di mame gezogt, oy, ikh hob fargesn tsu farshlisn di tir.

00:13:24.932 --> 00:13:27.001
ye dos iz geven. hob ikh gezogt,

00:13:27.058 --> 00:13:32.351
nokh di krig, ikh vel forn keyn Poyln, eb ikh nemen a bild fun di tir. di tir iz nokh dort do.

00:13:32.728 --> 00:13:38.426
ven ikh bin tsurikgeforn keyn Poyln, hob ikh gedenkt az ikh bin bay mayn seykhl,

00:13:38.854 --> 00:13:41.261
az ikh bin nisht nervezh, ikh hob azoy gedenkt.

00:13:41.487 --> 00:13:48.309
ikh hob fargesn di tir, un ikh bin geven azoy m'zogt DRUGGED UP. azoy vi oyf DRUGS.

00:13:48.309 --> 00:13:53.782
ikh hob nisht gevu- yetst volt ikh gevolt nokh eyn mol ahin forn di andere shtot,

00:13:53.805 --> 00:14:01.055
shteyn tsvey teg, un arayngeyn famelekh, onkukn nokh a mol, BECAUSE az ikh kuk dos on

00:14:01.332 --> 00:14:07.721
dermant zikh mir, un ikh glaykh zikh tsu dermanen fun di eltern un dos iz ales vos UNK tsu dermanen

00:14:07.795 --> 00:14:14.674
fun der tate, fun der mame, vu m'hot gelebt, iz dos iz undzer tate mame. bloyz di gedanken.

00:14:27.471 --> 00:14:31.717
un mir az s'kholemt zikh mir fun der heym, bin ikh tsufridn.

00:14:31.858 --> 00:14:37.776
s- ikh meyn ales az ikh bin in der heym. ober ikh vek zikh oyf, ze ikh s'nisht vor.

00:14:39.688 --> 00:14:42.922
zey hobn ruinirt dos lebn fun di eyropeishe yidn,

00:14:43.047 --> 00:14:47.428
un NO MATTER afile s'eyner gevorn a milyoner, tsi vos,

00:14:47.670 --> 00:14:51.191
s'kumt undz nisht iber. ikh ken mentshn vos zey hobn milyonen,

00:14:51.214 --> 00:14:55.227
azoy ven ikh, lomir zogn, ikh hob gemakht a progres in Amerike,

00:14:55.227 --> 00:15:01.721
ven ikh ken araynforn helfn der di mame, brider, a kuzin, di fargenign vos ikh volt gehat!

00:15:02.402 --> 00:15:07.458
un m'hot nisht, m'hot es nisht. zey hobn zey tseruinirt und efsher di kinder

00:15:07.515 --> 00:15:14.000
di kinder undzere ebn kenen lebn a normal lebn. undzer lebn iz shoyn nisht, NO.

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:16.453
m'lakht, dos iz ales gornisht vert.

00:15:17.067 --> 00:15:22.190
m'git zikh a derman fun der heym, iz es s'tsebrokhn.

00:15:23.378 --> 00:15:24.924
un dos vet shoyn nisht tsurikkumen.

00:15:26.618 --> 00:15:32.268
ikh kuk oyf bilder, ikh iber dem red ikh yidish. ikh vil zikh dermanen nor fun der heym.

00:15:32.268 --> 00:15:37.040
ikh bin in Amerike, tsu vemen ikh ken nor redn red ikh yidish, vayl ikh zikh dermanen fun der heym.

00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:41.394
ikh leyen a yidish bikhl, ikh tref bilder fun der heym, kuk ikh,

00:15:41.518 --> 00:15:46.856
er hot mir geshikt a bild, do in Argentine hob ikh es gehat a, der bruder hot mir gegebn a bild,

00:15:46.856 --> 00:15:51.486
vos shraybt fun nayntsn zeks un draysik iz es? akht un draysik,

00:15:51.981 --> 00:15:57.442
iz es bay mir azoy vi s'volt geven azoy vi ikh volt ⟨farlogt⟩ az m'volt mir gegebn a shtik gold.

00:15:57.533 --> 00:16:02.947
ikh kuk do oyf di datum, dos iz geven Tshmelev ven ikh hob gelebt mit di kuzinen, mitn tatn,

00:16:02.947 --> 00:16:05.947
ikh bin geven zeyer zeyer tsugebundn tsu der mame mayner.

00:16:06.527 --> 00:16:11.432
un m'hot zi gegebn a nem avek. kent ets farshteyn vi ikh hob gefilt?

00:16:12.214 --> 00:16:14.402
und di zakhn ken men nisht fargesn.

00:16:15.808 --> 00:16:19.109
di zakhn. yetst iz azoy. az ikh her redn doytsh,

00:16:19.588 --> 00:16:22.133
nisht vos ikh has di doytshn un ken mir nisht fartrogn.

00:16:22.133 --> 00:16:25.151
az ikh her geyn ban vos blozt di WHISTLE,

00:16:25.782 --> 00:16:29.896
dermants es mikh fun Aushvits, ken ikh oykhet nisht fartrogn. CERTAIN zakhn azelkhen

00:16:29.896 --> 00:16:35.934
vos dermant mikh di shlekhte tsaytn, dos ken ikh nisht. a ban az s'geyt, un di di di

00:16:36.733 --> 00:16:40.996
dos redn doytsh azoy, ken ikh nisht derlaydn.

00:16:41.340 --> 00:16:43.708
ober ikh has nisht ale doytshn, ikh ken

00:16:43.708 --> 00:16:46.484
ikh ken redn mit a doytsh, er't darfn epes helfn,

00:16:46.484 --> 00:16:51.425
un oyb er iz nisht keyn antisemit eb ikh im helfn oykhet. ikh ebn, AS a mentsh.

00:16:51.600 --> 00:16:54.581
farkert, azoy vi ikh hob geholfn polyakn in Tshmelev.

00:16:54.604 --> 00:16:57.765
zi hot ge- oys getsaygt tsu mayn kuzin zi iz a antisemitke,

00:16:57.765 --> 00:17:01.331
hob ikh gevolt tsaygn az di yidn zenen nisht azoy vi zey denken,

00:17:01.371 --> 00:17:04.447
un ven ikh bin avekgeforn hot zi aleyn gezogt,

00:17:04.447 --> 00:17:10.274
zi hot zikh nisht forgeshtelt az yidn zenen azoy gut vi zi hot gezen bay undz, bay mir un mayn froy.

00:17:11.968 --> 00:17:17.361
mayn froy biz yetst ken zi nisht fartseyln di mayse vos zey hobn opgetun tsu ir FAMILY.

00:17:17.757 --> 00:17:21.767
geshosn a yunge shvesterl mit a bruder in a vald geshosn.

00:17:22.026 --> 00:17:25.546
un di gantse familye umgebrengt. un zi hot nisht keynemen.

00:17:26.059 --> 00:17:31.419
lomir zogn ikh hob a kuzin, oder a bruder, zi hot keynem iz nisht geblibn. keynem nisht.

00:17:34.902 --> 00:17:36.887
ir vilt nokh epes tsugebn?

00:17:37.011 --> 00:17:39.604
na ikh denk no-, na.

00:17:40.065 --> 00:17:44.652
shtendik dermant men zikh shpeter, ikh hob nokh zeyer a sakh tsu fartseyln.

00:17:44.652 --> 00:17:46.432
ven ikh vel avekgeyn fun danen,

00:17:46.432 --> 00:17:51.942
vayl fun azoy fil yor dos mit tsu makhn iz do a sakh a sakh zakhn tsu redn.

00:17:55.168 --> 00:17:58.245
ikh hob do- ikh hob dokh gehert in Aushvits vu ikh hob gearbet krematoryum,

00:17:58.245 --> 00:18:03.279
-shrign "shma yisroel!" tsu got. vu iz geven got? vu iz er geven? vu iz er geven?

00:18:03.606 --> 00:18:08.611
un yetst ikh veys. ikh ayngezen hob ikh azoy.

00:18:08.770 --> 00:18:15.868
di ale mentshn, nisht ale, CERTAIN mentshn fun mayn shtot vos zenen geven in der heym zeyer zeyer frum,

00:18:15.925 --> 00:18:19.322
zeyer frum, zenen zey yetst

00:18:19.322 --> 00:18:25.841
zey haltn nisht fun shabes. zey, ikh veys nisht tsu zey davenen afiles. zey hobn gehaltn di gesheftn ofn shabes oykhet.

00:18:26.556 --> 00:18:32.675
in der heym iz geven eyner eyner vos er hot gehat a a a SON IN LAW,

00:18:32.817 --> 00:18:35.494
zayn er hot geheyrat zayn froy, er iz geven a raykher yid,

00:18:35.618 --> 00:18:39.310
un un zayn's a tokhter hot gehat dem. er iz geven a kalike, eyner er hot geha-

00:18:39.310 --> 00:18:43.071
er hot gehaltn dos gesheft ofn in shabes. azo shtetl iz dos geven.

00:18:43.144 --> 00:18:45.098
hot er zikh dokh geshemt, der yid,

00:18:45.098 --> 00:18:49.646
hot er gezogt, vifl fardinstu in shabes? hot er im gezogt. ot zogt er, ikh vel dir gebn di gelt,

00:18:49.646 --> 00:18:51.963
un halt farmakht dos gesheft in shabes.

00:18:52.172 --> 00:18:55.574
azo shtetl opgehitn yeder eyner iz geven, Tshmelev.

00:18:58.399 --> 00:19:04.074
nokh a sakh zakhn vos ikh vel zikh dermanen shpeter. dem hoypt zakh,

00:19:04.074 --> 00:19:11.218
mit di filme, ikh hof, vet helfn tsu makhn veyniker veyniker nisht mer antisemitizm.

00:19:12.169 --> 00:19:14.475
un s'vet zikh endikn. ikh hob gemeynt

00:19:14.498 --> 00:19:18.812
ven ikh bin aroyf fun Aushvits, afile s'a goy, ikh vel fartseyln vos ikh hob mitgemakht,

00:19:19.223 --> 00:19:24.566
un zey ebn aynzen az s'nisht geven rikhtik, zey ebn zikh toyshn. ikh ze ayn,

00:19:24.741 --> 00:19:28.914
az s'nokh do zeyer zeyer a sakh, s'a shvere arbet ze ikh,

00:19:28.914 --> 00:19:33.172
nokh dos ibertsuarbetn, di ale antisemitn zoln zikh

00:19:33.347 --> 00:19:37.779
iberarbetn, zey zoln nisht hasn keyn yidn far far NO REASON.

00:19:37.937 --> 00:19:39.736
far NO REASON. vayl er iz a yid.

00:19:43.928 --> 00:19:49.170
ikh vil aykh danken zeyer zeyer far altsding vos ir hot do dertseylt.

00:19:51.724 --> 00:19:57.928
I'M GLAD ikh bin tsufridn az ikh hob gekent fartseyln,

00:19:58.153 --> 00:20:02.686
ibergelebt di krig un kumen redn tsu yidn un fartseyln di geshikhte,

00:20:02.862 --> 00:20:11.327
un az ets un az ets hot zikh gevolt tsuhern tsu mir fun mayne tsores vos ikh hob mitgemakht.

00:20:14.708 --> 00:20:19.545
AND az ets farshteyt undz. di naye GENERATIONS farshteyt undz,

00:20:19.585 --> 00:20:26.193
di ale yidn vos zenen mitgemakht azoy fil, az ets arbet mit undz hot undz geholfn a sakh nokh di krig.

00:20:26.352 --> 00:20:32.572
vayl m'hot nisht gehat keyn FAMILY vu tsu geyn. un ets hot undz geholfn.

00:20:32.697 --> 00:20:34.868
un ikh dank enk oykhet zeyer far dem.

00:20:42.028 --> 00:20:46.241
di bild iz gemakht gevorn in Tshmelev in der heym in Poyln.

00:20:46.703 --> 00:20:55.286
FROM rekhts tsu links. der ershter in der rekhter zayt bin ikh Leybl Sherman. yetst iz Lion Sherman.

00:20:55.427 --> 00:21:01.041
in der mitn iz mayn shvester Tsarke, Sara Sherman.

00:21:01.924 --> 00:21:11.655
un in di lebn di shvester di shvester shteyt mayn bruder Tsvi Hasha Sherman, vos er lebt in Argentine.

00:21:12.032 --> 00:21:18.219
in der fornt iz mayn yingster bruder Nakhmen Sherman.

00:21:21.955 --> 00:21:26.556
er iz geven der yingster bruderl veys ikh iz geve- hot gemuzt zayn bay

00:21:26.865 --> 00:21:32.546
zibn yor, akht yor, efsher zeks yor, ikh veys nisht genoy mit di mit di yorn.

00:21:32.957 --> 00:21:39.785
ikh bin geven dort efsher tsen yor, elef yor.

00:21:43.318 --> 00:21:49.826
do di bild iz gemakht gevorn oykhet in Tshmelev, ikh gloyb nayntsn akht un draysik,

00:21:51.351 --> 00:21:57.656
un m'hot dos geshikt, di bilder, iz alte bilder, hot men geshikt, m'hot gehat a mume in Boynes Ayres,

00:21:58.202 --> 00:22:04.777
hot geheysn Shukhman, un tatn's a shvester, un di bild hot men gefunen bay zey.

00:22:04.817 --> 00:22:11.156
fun rekhts tsu links. shteyt in rekhter zayt shteyt mayn bruder Hershl Sherman,

00:22:11.652 --> 00:22:16.792
in der mitn iz mayn kuzin Yosl Fishbeyn.

00:22:17.575 --> 00:22:22.614
un in gantsn links iz Arye Grinboym, oykhet a kuzin.

00:22:22.789 --> 00:22:26.259
s'gemakht gevorn in Tshmelev nayntsn akht un draysik.

00:22:26.907 --> 00:22:30.090
es brengt mir oykhet tsurik a sakh MEMORIES.

00:22:34.264 --> 00:22:41.306
do iz mayn kuzin vos er iz in der mitn Yosl Fishbeyn, er hot dos geshikt tsu di mume

00:22:41.306 --> 00:22:48.242
un er shraybt tsu keyn Boynes Ayres in nayntsn akht un draysik, er shraybt do vi er fregt zi tsi zi gedenkt im,

00:22:48.242 --> 00:22:54.305
mit alem, un er zogt er gedenkt zey oy-, er gedenkt di mume ven zi iz avekgeforn keyn Argentine oykhet.

00:22:56.117 --> 00:23:02.372
s'zeyer a vikhtike bild far undz tsu dermanen undz vi in der heym.

00:23:05.837 --> 00:23:09.324
dos bild iz fun mayn mame olev-asholem.

00:23:09.432 --> 00:23:15.551
dos bild hot a HISTORY, di bild iz shoyn gemakht a COPY fun der ORIGINAL,

00:23:15.642 --> 00:23:18.724
dos bild hob ikh adurkhgeshmuglt in Aushvits.

00:23:19.084 --> 00:23:24.546
adurkh getrogn in in di CAMPS, un ikh hob es azoy gevatsht,

00:23:24.687 --> 00:23:29.450
akhtung gebn oyf dem biz biz yetst.

00:23:29.450 --> 00:23:33.154
un s'iz gevorn zeyer far- farkneytsht,

00:23:33.154 --> 00:23:36.492
hob ikh avekgegebn tsu makhn a COPY fun di ORIGINAL.

00:23:36.921 --> 00:23:40.324
un dos iz der bild fun di mame mayne.

00:23:43.063 --> 00:23:47.967
un dos iz zi heyst Perle Sherman.

00:23:48.987 --> 00:23:51.461
fun di NEE Grinbaum.

00:23:55.180 --> 00:23:59.834
dos bild iz in nayntsn ikh gloyb nayntsn dray un nayntsik, ven s'iz geven

00:23:59.834 --> 00:24:05.450
ANNIVERSARY fun Varshever Geto UPRISING, fun dem oyfshtand.

00:24:05.608 --> 00:24:11.930
ze'mir geforn ahin far a yortsayt vi m'zogt, geven a sakh fun Yisroel,

00:24:12.021 --> 00:24:16.582
un fun Amerike, fun Argentine, fun ale lender, un do vu ikh shtey do,

00:24:16.582 --> 00:24:19.743
der plats iz geven der krematoryum in Treblinka,

00:24:19.902 --> 00:24:28.941
un oyf dem ort intervyuirt mikh fun Nyu York TELEVISION, Bil Byutel. kanal NUMBER zibn.

00:24:29.098 --> 00:24:37.192
hot mikh do oysgefregt oykhet vegn di ts- vos vegn Aushvits, vegn di fargangenheyt do yetst.

00:24:41.653 --> 00:24:48.515
do iz oykhet in Treblinka, un dos iz mayn froy ven m'iz gekumen

00:24:48.640 --> 00:24:53.847
tsu di yortsayt fun fuftsik yor fun oyfshtand in Varshe,

00:24:54.090 --> 00:24:59.740
zi shteyt bay eyne fun di shteyner fun fun di yidn vos zenen umgekumen in Poyln,

00:24:59.740 --> 00:25:04.296
di andere Tshekhoslovakye, und zi heyst

00:25:04.296 --> 00:25:09.980
Khane Sherman yetst fun Mir, un fun der heym Honikman.

00:25:10.020 --> 00:25:16.309
zi hot oykhet farloyrn a yingere shvester un a eltern bruder,

00:25:16.315 --> 00:25:19.920
vos polyakn hobn zey geshosn in vald, hot zi oysgefunen,

00:25:19.926 --> 00:25:27.244
un di gantse familye umgekumen und un zi keyner iz nisht geblibn fun ir FAMILY.

00:25:27.351 --> 00:25:32.120
zi hot nisht keyn kuzin, keyner nisht, un zi ken zikh nokh nisht

00:25:32.177 --> 00:25:40.325
tsuzamen kumen zol kenen TESTIFY, fartseyln vos zi hot zi hot ibergelebt AS a kristin, AS a polke.

00:25:40.325 --> 00:25:48.556
zi iz geforn keyn Doytshland, zi kukt oys vi a shikse, a poylishe shikse, un zi hot ibergelebt nisht AS a yidishe.

00:25:48.833 --> 00:25:54.938
ikh hob in Nyu York hob ikh ir arbets kart vos zi hot gekrign, ikh hob es gekrign fun a bogado fun Poyln,

00:25:54.938 --> 00:26:01.499
fun Doytshland, fun Berlin. vu mit dem hakn-kroyt vu zi hot gea- v- in pletser vu zi hot gearbet,

00:26:01.573 --> 00:26:08.485
oykhet und vi yung zi iz geven damolts un vi zi hot oysgezen, ales oyf dem PASS.

00:26:08.492 --> 00:26:12.806
a shod ikh hob im nisht mitgebrengt mit zikh enk tsu tsaygn, az ikh vel kenen makhn a COPY

00:26:12.880 --> 00:26:22.273
eb ikh es aher shikn tsu enk deye arbets-kart, un oyb Spilberg's grupe vil dos zen, hob ikh es in Nyu York.

00:26:22.600 --> 00:26:26.588
oykhet oyb er vil zen, ikh hob papirn fun nokh di krig,

00:26:26.588 --> 00:26:33.731
ikh hob genumen fun Aushvits fun fun mir vos ikh bin geven registrirt dort, figirir ikh.

00:26:37.551 --> 00:26:40.062
dos iz mayn bruder Hershl Sherman.
